        <item>
            <title>2.2.5</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:21:14 -0400</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/hoomanaskari/mac-dictate-anywhere</link>
            <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.2.5</h1>
<ul>
<li>Updated the default AI cleanup prompt for Ollama and OpenRouter to better preserve final intent, structure dictated text, and normalize spoken numbers.</li>
<li>New installations now start with the recommended cleanup prompt instead of a blank field, while keeping the prompt fully customizable.</li>
<li>Updated the FluidAudio integration for compatibility with the current build toolchain.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
