        <item>
            <title>2.2.4</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 11:02:16 -0400</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/hoomanaskari/mac-dictate-anywhere</link>
            <sparkle:version>15</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.2.4</h1>
<ul>
<li>Fixed a startup issue where the global hotkey could fail to register immediately after launch or login.</li>
<li>Improved startup reliability by retrying audio engine preparation when FluidAudio is not ready on the first attempt.</li>
<li>Updated FluidAudio to 0.12.5.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
