        <item>
            <title>2.2.3</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 17:18:26 -0400</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/hoomanaskari/mac-dictate-anywhere</link>
            <sparkle:version>14</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.2.3</h1>
<ul>
<li>Restored the live overlay transcript preview when using OpenRouter transcript processing.</li>
<li>Removed the temporary OpenRouter audio upload path and returned OpenRouter to transcript-only post-processing.</li>
<li>Audio is transcribed locally again before any optional OpenRouter cleanup runs.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
